## 📄 Usage

### ▶️ Run the Script

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Right-click on `add-host.bat`
3. Select **Run as Administrator**

> ⚠️ Administrator privileges are required to modify the Windows hosts file

---

After running the script, you’ll be prompted:

### 🧑‍💻 Add a Domain


Mac / Linux
1. chmod +x HostManager.sh
2. sudo ./HostManager.sh

It will ask for Local Domain Name

# & It's Good to Go !
